<HEADLINE> Hipple Named LTV Steel President  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    CLEVELAND (AP) -- Richard J. Hipple, an LTV Corp. executive vice president,
has been appointed to the additional position of president of the LTV Steel Co.
division.
</P>
<P>
	   As LTV Steel president, Hipple, 47, will direct the flat-rolled steel
operations, raw materials and related joint ventures.
</P>
