	   The appointment announced Monday completes a new corporate structure in
which each major LTV unit is led by a president. In addition to flat-rolled
steel, there are divisions for Copperweld tubular steel and steel building
products.
</P>
<P>
	   Hipple, who was trained as a civil engineer, joined LTV Steel in 1975 and
became a corporate executive vice president in 1998.
