<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-10 20:51 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Bush, McCain Spar Over Taxes  </HEADLINE>
   By RON FOURNIER AP Political Writer
<TEXT>
<P>
	   GRAND RAPIDS, Mich. (AP) -- Gov. George Bush described himself Monday night
as ``a tax cutting person'' who delivered in Texas and would as president, while
